---
/**
 * What is Branding? - Custom Section for Branding Service Page
 * Educational content explaining branding concepts and value
 */
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-4 md:px-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50 to-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-cyan-900 leading-tight mb-6">
          What is <span class="text-orange-400">Branding?</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
            Branding is far more than just a logo or a color scheme—it's the complete identity and personality of your business.
            It encompasses every visual element, message, and experience that shapes how people perceive and remember your company.
            A strong brand creates emotional connections, builds trust, and differentiates you in the marketplace.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
            Effective branding combines strategic thinking with creative execution. It starts with understanding your business goals,
            target audience, competitive landscape, and unique value proposition. From there, we craft visual and verbal
            identities that authentically represent who you are and resonate with the people you want to reach.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
            At Codebrand, we approach branding holistically. We don't just design logos—we build complete brand systems that
            include strategy, positioning, visual identity, messaging frameworks, and comprehensive guidelines. This ensures
            your brand remains consistent, recognizable, and impactful across every touchpoint and channel.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-900 to-orange-400 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white">
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Elements of a Strong Brand</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <strong>Brand Strategy:</strong> Clear positioning, messaging, and personality that guides all decisions
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <strong>Visual Identity:</strong> Logo, color palette, typography, and design system that create recognition
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <strong>Brand Voice:</strong> Consistent tone, messaging, and communication style across all content
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <strong>Brand Experience:</strong> Every interaction and touchpoint that reinforces brand perception
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <strong>Brand Guidelines:</strong> Comprehensive documentation ensuring consistency across all applications
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path d="M10 3.5a1.5 1.5 0 013 0V4a1 1 0 001 1h3a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-.5a1.5 1.5 0 000 3h.5a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-.5a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0v.5a1 1 0 01-1 1H6a1 1 0 01-1-1v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1h-.5a1.5 1.5 0 010-3H4a1 1 0 001-1V6a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 001-1v-.5z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-900 mb-3">Brand Recognition</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Strong branding creates instant recognition. When customers can identify your business at a glance,
          you build familiarity and trust that leads to preference and loyalty over competitors.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cyan-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3.172 5.172a4 4 0 015.656 0L10 6.343l1.172-1.171a4 4 0 115.656 5.656L10 17.657l-6.828-6.829a4 4 0 010-5.656z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-900 mb-3">Emotional Connection</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Brands that resonate emotionally create lasting relationships. Through authentic storytelling and consistent
          messaging, we help you connect with your audience on a deeper, more meaningful level.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6 6V5a3 3 0 013-3h2a3 3 0 013 3v1h2a2 2 0 012 2v3.57A22.952 22.952 0 0110 13a22.95 22.95 0 01-8-1.43V8a2 2 0 012-2h2zm2-1a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v1H8V5zm1 5a1 1 0 011-1h.01a1 1 0 110 2H10a1 1 0 01-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            <path d="M2 13.692V16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2v-2.308A24.974 24.974 0 0110 15c-2.796 0-5.487-.46-8-1.308z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-900 mb-3">Business Value</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Strong brands command premium pricing and customer loyalty. Investing in professional branding builds
          long-term business value and creates a foundation for sustainable growth and success.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
